Wishing you an abundant 2023 filled with love, joy, real friends, money, adventure, & obviously 👉Solar☀️ If you are a musician or producer in California who owns a home with a home studio or own a studio building or rehearsal space, this year you probably noticed your already high electric bills, doubled,  putting your highest months over the $600 mark at the least.  Same goes for anyone who works in film or photography or potentially has a large fish tank in their Beverly Hills home that needs special lighting 24/7. I am here to help, and do my due diligence of making sure you all are aware that this is the last few months ( until April ) where you can save ( make ) money by going solar. If you live in California and you wait, you will be stuck with your increasing electric bills and won’t be given a second chance to take advantage of the current programs because again, THEY ARE ENDING FOREVER.  Please reach out if you’d like to know more about how to go solar & take advantage of this last opportunity ❤️ love you all my friends ❤️ ps successful referrals produce successful dollars in your pockets xx
